Patchset Numbering Scheme
=========================

1xxx Bug fixes
2xxx Security fixes
3xxx Arch-specific compatibility
4xxx Important features (for live-cd mode)
5xxx Nice-to-have features / fixes / addons

Individual Patch Descriptions
=============================

Patch: 4000_grml_logo.diff
Descr: use grml.org-logo in framebuffer
From:  http://dufo.tugraz.at/~prokop/grml-kernel/2.6.13-patches/grml_logo.diff

