Descr: Driver to support squashfs filesystems.
From:  http://dev.gentoo.org/~dsd/genpatches/trunk/2.6.14/4705_squashfs-2.2.patch
       http://mesh.dl.sourceforge.net/sourceforge/squashfs/squashfs2.2-r2.tar.gz

